{"tid":1578384,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet成員Irene面相冠絕韓藝界　大師稱「金相」瞓喺度都贏","createTime":"2019-09-18T06:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T09:41:24.000Z","uid":152123,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0745a93834925c366e134abfe046e5ba79f2f0dd","tid":1578384,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3285667/org/efd7e1417f99f3c20db1df2e875adb4c.jpg/4RfvyeNiE-MKJr0YGx9cWIXj7N9PsGG9CVhazwlYWs8?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3285667%2Forg%2Fefd7e1417f99f3c20db1df2e875adb4c.jpg%2F4RfvyeNiE-MKJr0YGx9cWIXj7N9PsGG9CVhazwlYWs8%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=a2403dec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國人與中國人一樣非常注意風水命理，面相也是他們非常重視的一環。近日韓國節目《TMI News》就請來面相學家，分析各7名面相最好的男女K-Pop偶像，沒想到Red Velvet隊長Irene不單止是整容範本的第一名外，更是被稱為「金相」，就連命理大師都認證的最強福相。<br />\n<br />\n經面相學家的一輪分析後，結果得出面相最好的7位女偶像順次序為Red Velvet Irene、宋佳人、請夏、ITZY Yeji、MAMAMOO華莎、TWICE志效和Sulli雪莉；而7位男偶像順次序則為BTS防彈少年團RM、姜丹尼爾、ASTRO車銀優、GOT7珍榮、WINNER宋旻浩、Golden Child普閔和X1金曜漢，位位都是現時當紅的人氣偶像。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據大師的分析，如果眼型如「貓眼」一樣向上揚，代表她能夠容易獲得大家的好感，並在對方心中留下強烈的印象。<br />\n<br />\n韓國女生習慣畫一字眉，可是大師講到帶有弧度的眉型才是最有福相。<br />\n<br />\n如果你同華莎一樣，面頰上有墨的話，恭喜你也是一位容易獲得成功的人。<br />\n<br />\n人人都說額頭最緊要有肉，這句說話亦有它的道理。根據大師所說，額頭圓潤的女生都屬感情較豐富。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIrene獲「金相」　一生獲貴人幫忙<br />\n<br />\n而榮登面相冠軍的Irene又有甚麼過人之處呢？Irene一直是韓國整容範本的第一名，她的神顏更被稱為仙女，出道以來都是Red Velvet的中心。大師分析Irene的眼睛頭尾尖銳，中間部分卻非常圓，稱之為「孔雀眼」。有孔雀眼的女生在任何場合都是集中的視線外，亦能輕易獲得大家的愛。而Irene修長而清秀的眉型，則象徵桃花及人緣好。總合她的五官和鵝蛋型臉型，學家稱Irene為「金相」，一世都有貴人的幫忙外，亦算是只有成功的命理。大師更講到Irene算是「瞓喺度都贏」的人，如果不在臉上動手術，她一生也是做藝人偶像的體質。"},{"pid":"76ce177418fb007ad8954f06f9bf17d396cc728a","tid":1578384,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:13:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5945f697b8b1c86082bb5993cd838b6d4661c3f2","tid":1578384,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:30:51.000Z","msg":"雖然我係red velvet 粉絲 但係我認為Irene 應該退出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1574057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1574057</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bceada71f11e8aa7a5998ae18167c1042a63e92f","tid":1578384,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"牙現志效令"},{"pid":"eda00181b10f2be14e5da654c5da66f1183bbd94","tid":1578384,"uid":76632,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:35:59.000Z","msg":"RM竟然上榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tF6tM1j.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtF6tM1j.gif&h=740d11df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"627a61c23c934988e5f86dc70e4149a355503971","tid":1578384,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"鼻頭好有肉 內心就冇毒<br />\n眼睛水汪汪 桃花運暢旺<br />\n眉尾散 儲錢難<br />\n上唇厚重情 下唇厚比較重性"},{"pid":"204a827d9ffd63d1d81a1acb43a03eba4e06452e","tid":1578384,"uid":152123,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bce